# Command:
#   mbm_copy
#
# Purpose:
#   Macro to apply mbcopy to all files referenced through
#   a datalist, using the MB-System file suffix convention
#   to name the output files. 
#
# Basic Usage: 
#   mbm_copy -Foutputformat -Idatalist [-H -V -C -T]
